{"talk":{"id":8530,"name":"Ben Cort: What commercialization is doing to cannabis","description":"In 2012, Colorado legalized cannabis and added to what has fast become a multibillion-dollar global industry for all things weed-related: from vape pens to brownies and beyond. But to say that we've legalized marijuana is subtly misleading -- what we've really done is commercialized THC, says educator Ben Cort, and that's led to products that are unnaturally potent. In an eye-opening talk, Cort examines the often unseen impacts of the commercial cannabis industry -- and calls on us to question those who are getting rich off of it.","slug":"ben_cort_what_commercialization_is_doing_to_cannabis","recorded_at":"2017-11-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-09-05 15:04:26","updated_at":"2021-06-17 15:09:13","viewed_count":1786460,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":444,"name":"TEDxMileHigh"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/efe86c6242c1b328b7a58b0c25d25b738a7af276_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/efe86c6242c1b328b7a58b0c25d25b738a7af276_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/efe86c6242c1b328b7a58b0c25d25b738a7af276_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/efe86c6242c1b328b7a58b0c25d25b738a7af276_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/dc0528e8d7c94c1d0f5ac9979187a3c25529c69a_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/BenCort_2017X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7972130,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/BenCort_2017X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":22123353,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/BenCort_2017X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc9